snippet.title: Pregnant Jennifer Lawrence Glows At ‘Don’t Look Up’ Premiere
snippet.description:
Soon-to-be mom Jennifer Lawrence stunned while hitting the red carpet at the New York City premiere of "Don't Look Up" on Sunday, where she was joined by other members of the A-list cast including Leonardo DiCaprio, Jonah Hill and Meryl Streep
